FRANCE DAYBOOK: Sarkozy, Berlusconi Meet Over Immigrants

-- B y  
-- 
2011-04-26T04:08:46Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-26/france-daybook-sarkozy-berlusconi-meet-over-immigrants.html
Italian Prime Minister  Silvio
Berlusconi  and French President Nicolas Sarkozy meet today as
bilateral disputes over immigration and corporate takeovers add
strains to European unity.  ALL TIMES CET  WHAT TO WATCH:
*Sarkozy And Berlusconi Press Conference in Rome at 1 p.m.
*Sarkozy may disclose his views on Bank of Italy Governor Mario
Draghi’s bid to replace  Jean-Claude Trichet  at the head of the
 European Central Bank  in tomorrow’s briefing in Rome  AM EARNINGS
* Air Liquide (AI FP) 1Q revenue 7:30 a.m.  PM EARNINGS
* April Group (APR FP) 1Q revenue 5:30 p.m.
* Renault SA (RNO FP) 1Q revenue 5:30 p.m.
* SEB (SK FP) 1Q revenue 5:30 p.m.
* Seche Environnement (SCHP FP) 1Q revenue 5:30 p.m.
* Sopra (SOP FP) 1Q revenue 5:30 p.m.  ECONOMY: Data and events today  GOVERNMENT:
* France-Italy summit in Rome  EQUITIES:
*Michelin & Cie. (ML FP): The world’s second-largest tiremaker
said first-quarter revenue rose 28 percent.
*French carmakers  Renault SA (RNO)  and PSA Peugeot Citroen will
finish paying back the 6 billion euros they borrowed from the
country’s government earlier than expected  MARKETS:
*The CAC 40 Index rose 0.43 percent to 4,021.88
*The broader SBF 120 Index rose 0.42 percent to 3,015.64  INTERVIEWS ELSEWHERE:
-07:50 France 2: Corinne Lepage, former presidential candidate
